<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV62">
<l>iṟaiyō virakkiṉu mīṅkōrpeṇ pāleṉa vumiraṅkā</l>
<l>taṟaiyō veṉaniṉ ṟatiruṅ karuṅkaṭa līṅkivaṭaṉ</l>
<l>ṉiṟaiyō viṉiyuṉ tiruvaru ḷālaṉṟik kāpparitāṉ</l>
<l>muṟaiyō varavaṇai mēṟpaḷḷi koṇṭa mukilvaṇṇaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Here, with the black ocean thundering constantly as if it was blows, without</l>
<l>pity though speaking here to one of female gender, even if she pleads “lord!”,</l>
<l>her plumpness, it is difficult to guard now, except by your holy grace.</l>
<l>Is that in order, you of cloud colour who takes rest on the serpent bed?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
